qts, Quick Torrent Search

A Firefox and Chrome add-on that enables you to search for torrents directly
from the context menu. Simply select some text, right click, and search for
torrents on your favorite site.

https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/quick-torrent-search

https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ohimefjlbhbgnegmdmnheidlgmelilii
